For some reason, Katy is really bothering me. I mean, she doesn't sing this well by any means, but she developed herself as an "artist." So, she's telling this girl that she has to develop herself as an artist, and she sounds competitive in her tone to me. She seems like a very insecure person underneath all that kind of stern approach to a lot of the contestants. She should be hooping and hollering over this girl, ,but she isn't.

This girl IS ALREADY singing with great artistry. Katy has heard her sing ONE song. What does she know about what this girl has done. She didn't even ask her whether or not she writes her own music!
Sorry, but lately, she bugs that crap out of me. This young 17 year old girl sings circles around Katy Perry. She might never wear short skirts and bras that squirt while on stage like Katy did/does, but I think that is a HUGE PLUS!! Just look at Kelly Clarkson. She never used those gimmicks and her voice carried her through. Without the gimmicks, Katy wouldn't have gone anywhere, because although she can sing ok, she isn't a great singer. Neither is Brittany Spears. Same thing... Gimmicks. UGH...I wish Katy Perry could be more humble and admit that she just doesn't have it all.
